# Database Rules

## Database Provider

Neon PostgreSQL

## ORM

Drizzle ORM

## Primary Keys

- UUID

## Requirements

- Foreign Key Constraints
- Database Indexes
- Soft Deletes when appropriate
- Schema defined in `src/db/schema.ts`
- Migrations managed via Drizzle Kit (`drizzle/migrations/`)

## Never

- Store images inside database
- Store large files inside database
- Duplicate user data
- Use Supabase client or raw SQL without Drizzle (except migrations)

## Images

- Cloudflare R2 only

## Tables

- users
- cars
- car_images
- favorites

## Optimize for

- 100,000+ users
- Fast search
- Low cost

All queries must be optimized and indexed. Use Drizzle relational queries where appropriate.
